{"tid":2208832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美擬售台七武器 包括導彈無人機","createTime":"2020-09-19T08:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T08:17:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f1f777ae974b46eeacdc71d8126bfa6a8e1937cc","tid":2208832,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:16:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200917/XO2Q423BJFF3LOSCGM7VFQJDXM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200917%2FXO2Q423BJFF3LOSCGM7VFQJDXM%2F&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdChjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=fd55ffcb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200917%2FXO2Q423BJFF3LOSCGM7VFQJDXM%2F&h=07b86bfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200917/XO2Q423BJFF3LOSCGM7VFQJDXM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美擬售台七武器 包括導彈無人機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OEjpi_AazGIODcrO8YrHqu201fk=/600x315/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZY5P3YGZLBB2XEKB6TSEJ75HXE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOEjpi_AazGIODcrO8YrHqu201fk%3D%2F600x315%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZY5P3YGZLBB2XEKB6TSEJ75HXE.jpg&h=ab671a57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n路透社引述消息報道，美國計劃向台灣再出售多達七種武器，包括水雷、巡航導彈及無人機，以加大對北京施壓。台灣國防部（圖）昨晚回應，此為媒體臆測，對於評估或洽談中軍購案，均秉持低調保密原則，依例不公開說明。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n令台灣像「刺蝟」 防範北京<br />\n<br />\n報道指，隨着北京在區域內的軍事動作日益積極，華府欲以「台灣堡壘」（Fortress Taiwan）計劃，在軍事上制衡北京。報道引述軍售消息人士指出，涉及的武器來自波音、洛歇馬丁及通用原子航空系統公司。美國國務卿蓬佩奧預定本周向特朗普做簡報，其中部分武器是台灣在一年多前提出採購，但直到現在才進入審批。<br />\n<br />\n有美國官員指，台灣。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社形容，此次美國尋求向台灣一次性出售七種武器，是打破多年來慣例的罕見做法。以往美對台軍售總是分散進行、謹慎規劃，以盡量使其與北京之間的緊張關係最小化。但特朗普政府今年對中國更為強硬，此次軍售正值「中美關係處於幾十年來的最低谷」之際。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部月初發佈中國軍力報告，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/中央社"},{"pid":"1e9bfb490e259ce1d84f76d425d626db2e36ec7d","tid":2208832,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:17:10.000Z","msg":"支那:好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}